description: [``botocore``] Releasing new APIs related to Tuning steps in model building pipelines.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for ML Explainability to display model variable importance value in Amazon Fraud Detector.

[``botocore``] MediaConvert now supports color, style and position information passthrough from 608 and Teletext to SRT and WebVTT subtitles. MediaConvert now also supports Automatic QVBR quality levels for QVBR RateControlMode.
